## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0a9a0-102">当创建需要调用方身份验证和/或授权的 [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] 应用程序时，您可以指定记录与安全相关的事件的成功或失败情况，或同时记录两者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0a9a0-102">When creating a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] application that requires authentication and/or authorization of the callers, you can specify that events related to security be recorded for either success, failure, or both.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0a9a0-103">审核的级别由此枚举决定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0a9a0-103">The level of auditing is determined by this enumeration.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0a9a0-104">指定审核日志的位置的方法是：通过将 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.AuditLogLocation%2A> 类的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> 属性设置为 <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLogLocation> 值之一。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0a9a0-104">The location of the audit log is specified by setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.AuditLogLocation%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> class to one of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLogLocation> values.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0a9a0-105">有关审核的详细信息，请参阅[审核](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/auditing-security-events.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0a9a0-105">For more information about auditing, see [Auditing](~/docs/framework/wcf/feature-details/auditing-security-events.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0a9a0-106">你还可以指定审核行为使用[ &lt;serviceSecurityAudit&gt; ](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/servicesecurityaudit.md)绑定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0a9a0-106">You can also specify audit behavior using the [&lt;serviceSecurityAudit&gt;](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/servicesecurityaudit.md) binding.</span></span>  
  
   
  
